Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫大人  醒了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒是醒了  但慢慢起床的時間還是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是Union Fasta的最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城裡面又是熱鬧得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典要結束了好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快樂的時光就不能一直持續下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
