Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送還三位勇者的預定日期定在了Union Fasta結束之後的三天后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.29,0:02:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離別之日馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…謝謝你蕾貝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特意過來送我一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天七海和公主大人去了比斯科迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久和庫蓓爾在帕斯提亞久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我去伽雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就好像是互換勇者似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我準備了點有趣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海和米爾希那邊肯定會很歡樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾貝卡你不來一件麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  現在為您進行現場直播
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Union Fasta的談話節目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時段的舞台嘉賓是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比斯科迪共和國代表領主  米爾希奧蕾公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:19.18,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伽雷特獅子團傑諾瓦茲的三位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是這位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比斯科迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比斯科迪的勇者  高槻七海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…那個  勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼感覺和平時不太一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢  趁著這個機會  今天七海來當我的勇者了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說一日勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾恩殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Union Fasta也到了最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次活動的直到現在的結果怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無疑問  到現在為止的成績非常的好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高爾殿下  那麼對於勇者大人您怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁這個機會問她本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我國勇者在此登場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是伽雷特的勇者蕾貝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天蕾貝卡是我伽雷特的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exmachina也當然是仿造品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾貝卡大人好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海大人和蕾貝卡大人都扮演的很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說勇者大人將成為帕斯提亞久的一日勇者嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說衣服也都換成這邊的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔♂法♂光♂線
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這必然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒…倒也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…在各種意義上都算擦邊球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…大家這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  倒是挺合身嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一想必然是這種結果嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  很帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  到了勇者們該回去的時間了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  很快就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念啊  地球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們回去的時候我能不能一起去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還用說？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊女孩的體型和內衣都是什麼樣的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風太大沒聽清  什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  今晚的Final Stage敬請大家期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？諾瓦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和諾瓦還有莉科  現在要出個門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我們送一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  沒事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三個乘飛毯過去輕鬆得很
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  米爾希姐的演唱會前再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛毯  走起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來我們也往會場那邊走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕斯提亞久正統繼承者生物模式確認
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時確認天槍Coumars裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門即將打開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是艾森巴哈城的地下傳承寶物庫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為帕斯提亞久引以為傲的古代遺址  是個超大型迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有所耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是第一次能進到裡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆以前不是跟我說過想要在這裡探險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很小的時候的事兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的信條就是約好了就決不會忘也不會食言嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  一定要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個寶物庫有很多對付入侵者的陷阱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  只有地下才會有陷阱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樓的陷阱已經全部關閉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的庫大人  不要嚇我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是庫大人你自己難道有什麼事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我本來是來取送還儀式上要送給蕾貝卡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的回憶之物就放在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後莉科和諾瓦  你們不是經歷了上次的勇者送還嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想聽聽那個時候發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個寶箱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先先拿好這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛毯飛毯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝力開放•七尾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設置了陷阱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個地方已經很舊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼地方出了些問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是地下十層吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是垂直掉下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用飛毯的話很快就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  關上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被關在這裡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看那個的話肯定能找到通往出口的路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位  踩在地板上的時候一定要多加注意…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我話還沒說完就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這迷宮太累人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不趕緊出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好這裡有椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是這個難道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾貝卡  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了  總有種不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岔路口  有個岔路口就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管前面怎麼跑都是一條路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？貝琪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  庫大人跟你們匯合了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…還沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是那麼費時間的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡的地下？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是要去地下的寶物庫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個寶物庫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個地方原本是我作為魔王的時候建造的迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡頭佈滿各種各樣的邪惡殘忍的陷阱  是超贊的最終迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  陷阱都鎖住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  畢竟那些東西也有些年頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:11:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝琪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼我們稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉科  諾瓦  真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我把你們請來這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫大人  你這說的就不對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本想要來這裡的是我們才對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果我能夠再小心謹慎一些就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是當初仔細打理這個地方就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要那麼說的話  還得怪我當時你們剛掉下去的時候我沒能用七尾把你們抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在想如果當時能多多注意一下地面的陷阱就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  這是城堡的地下  到時候肯定會有人來救咱們的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  話說庫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於送還的事情你想問我們什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有在和勇者分別的時候感到寂寞或者感到不安什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是非常的寂寞和悲傷的  我哭了好長時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的送還也發生了很多很多的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  當知道了他還能再回來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的感覺就全部都消失不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對於七海和真久要回去的事情也感到很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但說真的  不知道什麼時候就又能見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  果然這過程還是會很不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾貝卡是遠方世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在故鄉也有很多有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有很多很多重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會直接忘了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾貝卡是個溫柔的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白那種事情是不會發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  別離還是很傷感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就儘管笑話我這個不值得信賴的  膽小又稚嫩的見習領主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會笑話你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟最喜歡的人分別卻不感到寂寞的人  這個世界上是不存在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  莉科  休息結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送還蕾貝卡大人之前剩下來的這點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你們兩個人能待在一起更長的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊從這裡出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉科  諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易我耍一回帥  別這樣對我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個  快看上面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爭取想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓我的兩個好朋友受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Coumars所在位置確認
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱暫時停止但撐不了太長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  蕾貝卡  快去救援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘  拿著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔人結晶  也就是說是英雄結晶的魔王版
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾貝卡的話肯定能用好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:15:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者  傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又開始掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能打開這扇門…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者真久的英雄時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者蕾貝卡現在抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾貝卡  真久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就把這東西給推回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  這東西好沉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  你先一個人支撐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:17:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔人結晶  發動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔人模式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女加農炮•超魔王模式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  快臥倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我飛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  真久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.53,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾貝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾貝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我早說過了要去危險的地方的時候一定要由我和騎士們同行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你沒事兒真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姑且也算是騎士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦  小聲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  快點從這裡離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人的演唱會快要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了正式開幕的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才大家都入座了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大家沒事兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點問題都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在歡笑中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我也就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我先回座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在帕斯提亞久當一天的勇者服…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對啊這是貝琪的！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.19,0:23:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是謝謝大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.30,0:23:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種彈性  真不愧是…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
